name: CASKAD #034
description:
CKD#034

C5 / F1 / NX / A1

CASKAD is a generative art series of drawings realised with the same program. The series correspond to 100 consecutive executions of the codes in which no parameters or results have been modified. Numerous variables have ranges in which they can evolve according to certain probabilities:

- Color
- Frame size
- Number of itterations
- Angular velocity

Are the features take into account for price at first sales and are based on program probabilities and not on actual probabilities occuring in this series.

Go check my twitter for global picture of what is coming next!

Hope you will like it ! 

/* Life is a waterfall of probabilities */
